Summary: 2 star-like objects moving fast from east to west in tandem
divs: sighting detailsit was around 10pm central time on 6\16\2011. i was outside, happen to be looking up. i could see commercial aircraft in the sky moving at their usual speed and altitude. i have seen satellites before. i have seen meteors of different sizes, speed, and color before. but i could not explain this. coming from slightly south east, 2 objects moving in tandem, one slightly in front of the other but moving at the same speed, curved slightly and headed due west, passing over the house and out of view. they were moving faster than the commercial aircraft currently in the sky. there was also no sound either before, during, or after they had passed. i am not sure what it was except unidentifiable. i have chosen to submit this brief sighting on this site in the hopes that others either east or west of me submit more information in the attempt to identify these objects.
